content:
To let agents and bots share files with customers in enhanced Messaging channels and Messaging for In-App and Web, configure your content delivery settings. This applies to Lightning Experience.

Available editions:
Messaging for In-App, Messaging for Web, enhanced WhatsApp, enhanced Facebook Messenger, enhanced SMS, enhanced Apple Messages for Business, and Bring Your Own Channel.

Required user permissions:
Customize Application (to enable content deliveries and public links)
Create Public Links

Configure Content Deliveries in Setup as follows:
Select the first two checkboxes
Choose either the first or second password protection option (third option causes an error)

Verify that Create Public Links is assigned to users who share files.
title: Enabling File Sharing for Enhanced Messaging Channels
